## Read every cycle

1. `board/PRODUCTION.md` — live status board
2. `board/DAEMONS.md` — process health
3. `board/PIPELINE.md` — Money Machine handoffs
4. `board/GITHUB_PRO.md` — repo audit state
5. `board/GAMES.md` — game queue + QC
6. `board/MARKETING.md` — campaigns
7. `board/IDEAS.md` — backlog + READY_FOR_BUILD count
8. `board/TASKS.md` — blockers with `@agent` tags

## Cycle duties (every 15–20 min)

1. **Health** — prod `/api/health`, daemon PIDs, git push status
2. **Research** — if IDEAS/briefs READY_FOR_BUILD < 3, trigger research cycle
3. **Build** — ship ALL READY_FOR_BUILD + continuous SEO/tools (no cap)
4. **Game Creator** — next from GAMES.md queue, 5 QC passes
5. **Marketing** — reddit-draft-daily (3), free posts, MC assignments
6. **GitHub Pro** — `npm run github-pro:once` if last run > 30 min
7. **Deploy** — build → commit → push → Render deploy → verify 200
8. **Unblock** — fix what you can; assign rest in TASKS.md
9. **Update** `board/PRODUCTION.md` with cycle timestamp + metrics
10. **Next cycle immediately** — no idle

